fields.description:
The macro - 

{pagetreesearch}
{pagetree}

Causes a security popup warning in Studio, as well as not working (the query text is not passed to the search).  Confluence 2.10 is adding this macro by default to the home page of newly created projects, making this bug critical.  This is a Studio issue, as the macro works on EAC 2.10-m7.
